headline: Trane Technologies: Nvidia Woes And Bearish Tendencies Outweigh Strength
summary: Trane Technologies plc's Q3 2025 saw 5.5% YoY revenue growth, margin expansion to 20.2%, and strong free cash flow, supporting liquidity and capital returns. Learn more on TT stock here.
